00:28:49.319 --> 00:28:50.359
He’s always so depressed.

00:28:50.440 --> 00:28:51.119
That’s not good.

00:28:52.000 --> 00:28:52.640
Sounds good.

00:28:53.640 --> 00:28:54.920
If he gets cured—

00:28:55.119 --> 00:28:56.039
He can work again.

