00:29:08.720 --> 00:29:09.119
Come on.

00:29:09.200 --> 00:29:10.599
Let’s all encourage him.

00:29:11.079 --> 00:29:12.039
Take it off.

00:29:12.359 --> 00:29:18.400
Take it off, take it off, take it off!

00:29:25.039 --> 00:29:25.559
Everyone—

00:29:26.200 --> 00:29:27.200
See you next time.

00:29:27.720 --> 00:29:29.079
I’ve got something to do, I’ll head out.

00:29:31.440 --> 00:29:32.359
Meng Hang.

00:29:33.000 --> 00:29:34.599
Meng Hang, Meng Hang, answer the phone!

00:29:36.920 --> 00:29:37.720
Is that you?

00:29:55.200 --> 00:29:56.559
What a coincidence, everyone’s here.

00:29:57.160 --> 00:29:57.759
Yeah.

00:29:58.599 --> 00:29:59.480
The mean one—

00:29:59.759 --> 00:30:00.559
Is here too.

00:30:14.680 --> 00:30:15.440
That’s rough.

00:30:16.519 --> 00:30:18.359
Your whole family takes turns hitting you.

00:30:19.119 --> 00:30:21.240
I should help you heal your trauma.

00:30:22.240 --> 00:30:23.799
Just shut up.

00:30:24.079 --> 00:30:26.599
Stop talking about your therapy.

00:30:27.759 --> 00:30:29.400
Just use your skills—

00:30:29.759 --> 00:30:31.400
Fix my bones, that’s enough.

00:30:32.599 --> 00:30:33.319
Don’t worry, don’t worry.

00:30:33.640 --> 00:30:34.240
Bone setting, sure.

00:30:34.599 --> 00:30:37.200
I’m a pro at bone setting and massage.

00:30:37.319 --> 00:30:37.799
Come on.

