Move over there a bit.

00:30:41.200 --> 00:30:41.799
Relax.

00:30:42.519 --> 00:30:43.119
Lift your face.

00:30:43.200 --> 00:30:44.119
Face, face, face.

00:30:45.759 --> 00:30:46.200
Relax.

00:30:46.559 --> 00:30:46.920
One.

00:30:47.319 --> 00:30:47.680
Two.

00:30:47.799 --> 00:30:48.200
Three.

00:30:51.000 --> 00:30:51.400
How’s that?

00:30:51.920 --> 00:30:52.599
Is it fixed?

00:30:56.759 --> 00:30:57.319
Yeah.

00:30:58.279 --> 00:30:59.039
It doesn’t hurt now.

00:30:59.759 --> 00:31:01.000
But why do I feel—

00:31:01.839 --> 00:31:02.960
My right side—

00:31:04.200 --> 00:31:05.440
Is numb.

00:31:17.640 --> 00:31:18.119
It’s fine.

00:31:18.640 --> 00:31:19.319
Totally normal.

00:31:19.839 --> 00:31:20.359
Totally normal.

00:31:21.240 --> 00:31:21.920
Let me get ready.

00:31:22.160 --> 00:31:23.039
I’ll do some acupuncture for you.

00:31:23.519 --> 00:31:24.839
Acupuncture works wonders.

00:31:25.240 --> 00:31:25.599
One poke—

00:31:25.640 --> 00:31:26.559
You’ll feel it instantly.

00:31:34.240 --> 00:31:34.960
Doctor.

00:31:36.000 --> 00:31:36.920
Are you ready?

00:31:41.440 --> 00:31:42.039
Doctor.

00:31:43.720 --> 00:31:44.640
Are you ready?

00:31:46.000 --> 00:31:46.880
Doctor.

00:31:47.319 --> 00:31:48.799
Are you ready?

00:31:50.720 --> 00:31:51.799
Doctor.

