Money cures heartache.

00:32:08.839 --> 00:32:09.400
My money—

00:32:09.480 --> 00:32:10.680
Is about to be recovered.

00:32:11.440 --> 00:32:12.559
The police contacted you.

00:32:12.839 --> 00:32:13.839
They messaged me.

00:32:14.000 --> 00:32:15.440
Asked me to send them the account.

00:32:15.480 --> 00:32:16.960
I sent them the account and password.

00:32:27.359 --> 00:32:28.680
Got three thousand back.

00:32:29.599 --> 00:32:30.440
That’s great!

00:32:30.680 --> 00:32:32.519
I knew you guys weren’t reliable.

00:32:32.880 --> 00:32:34.759
Look at their efficiency.

00:32:35.000 --> 00:32:35.799
Amazing.

00:32:37.119 --> 00:32:37.839
Thank you, thank you.

00:32:37.960 --> 00:32:39.160
Thank you, police.

00:32:43.440 --> 00:32:44.599
With that IQ—

00:32:45.240 --> 00:32:47.079
Who else would scammers target?

00:32:47.440 --> 00:32:49.359
You even pretended to be police and paid him.

00:32:49.480 --> 00:32:51.240
Totally unnecessary.

00:32:52.559 --> 00:32:53.920
Don’t let him hear that.

00:32:54.720 --> 00:32:57.000
I was worried his depression would get worse.

00:32:57.400 --> 00:32:58.400
This is great.

00:32:58.880 --> 00:33:00.000
Money solves everything.

