00:33:32.279 --> 00:33:32.839
They’d definitely—

00:33:32.960 --> 00:33:33.960
Be much better off.

00:33:34.279 --> 00:33:34.640
This—

00:33:34.640 --> 00:33:36.759
Is a unique trait of our home planet.

00:33:37.480 --> 00:33:39.200
I’ll keep observing closely—

00:33:39.279 --> 00:33:41.359
The cultural differences between Earthlings and us.

00:33:41.559 --> 00:33:42.559
This comparative study—

00:33:42.640 --> 00:33:43.839
For both civilizations—

00:33:43.920 --> 00:33:45.759
